To install rubwitter follow these steps:

1. cd to rubwitter folder.
2. Run "gem install bundler".
3. Run bundle install - this will install needed gems:

$> gem list --local

*** LOCAL GEMS ***

bundler (1.0.3)
git (1.2.5)
jeweler (1.5.1)
json (1.4.6)
mime-types (1.16)
oauth (0.4.4)
rake (0.8.7)
rcov (0.9.9)
rubwitter (0.1.1)
shoulda (2.11.3)
twitter_oauth (0.4.3)

4. Run "rake install".

5.. Run "rubwitter".

To start using rubwitter type "help" in command line interface.

Have a nice day!
